                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7441" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0229</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2999 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内外兼修，循次而进：五年改革中龙源环保如何实现治理机制的全面构建？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Internal and external training, step by step: how to achieve a comprehensive construction of governance mechanism in the reform of state-owned enterprises Longyuan Environmental Protection?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙梅，李健源，于晨</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油大学（北京）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国能龙源环保有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">24 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司治理机制；党组织；双百行；国企改革三年行动；中国特色现代企业制度</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Corporate Governance Mechanism, Party Organization, Double Hundred Action, Three-Year Action of SOE Reform, Modern Enterprise System with Chinese Characteristics</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有企业完善公司治理机制是全面推进依法治企、推进国家治理体系和治理能力现代化的内在要求，是实现企业高质量发展的根本保证。国有企业将党的领导与完善公司治理机制有机统一，推进思想融合、体制融合、机制融合、标准融合、监督融合，有助于形成权责明确、权责透明、协调运转、有效制衡的公司治理机制，提高企业运行效率，建立现代企业制度。本案例通过描述国能龙源环保有限公司2018-2022年期间，参加“双百行动”和“国企改革三年行动”时逐步探索内、外部治理机制的全面构建过程。引导学生掌握决策机制、激励机制和监督机制为主的内部治理机制和经理人市场化机制等外部治理机制，以及党组织在决策和监督方面嵌入治理机制的方式等相关的理论，并将此理论运用到企业公司治理机制的具体实践中，启发学生思考公司治理机制如何进行优化，推动国有企业高质量发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The improvement of corporate governance mechanisms in state-owned enterprises is an inherent requirement to comprehensively promote the governance of enterprises in accordance with the law and the modernization of the national governance system and governance capacity, and is a fundamental guarantee to achieve the high-quality development of enterprises. State-owned enterprises organically unify the leadership of the Party with the improvement of corporate governance mechanisms, promote the integration of ideas, institutions, mechanisms, standards and supervision, and help form a corporate governance mechanism with clear authority and responsibilities, transparent authority and responsibilities, coordinated operation and effective checks and balances, improve the operational efficiency of enterprises, and establish a modern enterprise system. This case describes the comprehensive process of building internal and external governance mechanisms that Guoneng Longyuan Environmental Protection Co., Ltd. has gradually explored during its participation in the &quot;Double Hundred Actions&quot; and the &quot;Three-Year Actions for State-owned Enterprises Reform&quot; during the period of 2018-2022. It guides students to master the theory of internal governance mechanism based on decision-making mechanism, incentive mechanism and supervision mechanism, external governance mechanism such as market-oriented mechanism for managers, and the way of embedding the Party organisation in the governance mechanism in terms of decision-making and supervision, and applies this theory to the specific practice of corporate governance mechanism of the enterprise, which inspires students to think about how to optimise the corporate governance mechanism and promote the high-quality development of state-owned enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理与内部控制》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党组织嵌入公司治理；决策机制；激励机制；监督机制；职业经理人</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
